cs.AI, cs.GIS, cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.CL

The paper discusses the recent development of AI with a focus on machine learning and deep learning approaches, which are commonly associated with the cs.AI and cs.LG sub-categories. The integration of AI with geography and particularly geographic information science is the main focus of the paper, which suggests that it could also belong to the cs.GIS sub-category. The paper also presents a number of GeoAI applications, which could be related to the cs.CV sub-category for computer vision and the cs.CL sub-category for natural language processing.
